{"ops":[{"insert":"基本用途"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"ExpandWrapper 是一个可展开/收起的 UI 组件，通常用于实现内容区域的折叠和展开功能，比如详情信息的隐藏/显示、选项卡的展开等场景。\n\n主要功能"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"1. 展开/收起切换：点击头部区域可以切换内容的显示和隐藏状态\n2. 旋转图标：包含一个三角形图标，会根据展开状态进行旋转（向下→向上）\n3. 自定义插槽：支持通过插槽自定义头部(header)和内容(content)部分\n4. 双向绑定：支持通过 `value` 属性和 `change` 事件实现 v-model 双向绑定\n5. 回调函数：提供 `onChange` 回调函数，在展开状态改变时触发\n\n基本用法"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"plain"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"<template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  <ExpandWrapper v-model=\"isExpanded\">"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    <template #header>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      <!-- 自定义头部内容 -->"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      点击我展开/收起"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    </template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    <template #content>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      <!-- 自定义内容部分 -->"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      这里是展开后显示的内容"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    </template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  </ExpandWrapper>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"<script>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"import ExpandWrapper from './expand-wrapper.tsx'"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"export default {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  components: {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    ExpandWrapper"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  },"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  data() {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    return {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"plain"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      isExpanded: false // 控制展开状态"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    }"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  }"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"}"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</script>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"\nProps 属性"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"- `value` (Boolean): 控制组件的展开状态，默认为 `false`（收起状态）\n- `onChange` (Function): 展开状态改变时的回调函数，参数为新的展开状态值\n\n事件"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"- `change`: 当展开状态改变时触发，参数为当前的展开状态（Boolean）\n\n插槽"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"- `header`: 自定义展开组件的头部内容（显示在可点击区域）\n- `content`: 自定义展开后显示的内容部分\n\n样式特点"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"- 头部区域有背景色 (#f0f1f5) 和边框 (#dcdee5)\n- 收起状态下内容区域不可见 (`display: none`)\n- 展开状态下三角形图标会旋转 90 度，从向下变为向上\n- 收起状态下底部边框会被隐藏，使外观更加整洁\n- 整个组件宽度为 100% ，适应父容器宽度\n\n该组件设计简洁，易于集成到各种项目中，特别适合需要节省空间、按需展示内容的场景。\n"}],"extra":{"updator":"Austin","update_at":"2026-01-21 15:10:50"}}